2018-07-16 16:02:09 Peter Fox <peter.rd.fox@gmail.com> socket/unixsocket/src/main/java/com/github/tessera/socket/SocketExecutor.java v 91bc0bb33205ecb5f4c950b78e5319cb97de91a6

Move a general executor into the main application, which other
libraries can provide runnable classes for. The context (which is
currently Spring) submits the runnable actions to the executor.

This allows for less duplication, since the same executor logic doesn't
need to be duplicated across modules.
